{"title":"大寨民歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1975,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是宝中宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的书是宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民离不了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握这个宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山能移来水能调；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握这个宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社粮堆比山高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握这个宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政牢又牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠党领导"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨步步高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处新面貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是天赐给，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠党领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中有了大目标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中没有大目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根谷草压弯腰；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中有了大目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤重担也敢挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读马列和毛主席的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读了马列和毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心明眼亮步不差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级革命路线指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里浪里识真假。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认准一条道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义认真学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基本路线记得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里认准一条道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义俺们走定了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱什么恨什么要明显"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红线黑线两条线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱什么恨什么要明显。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红线是咱生命线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱要爱在心里边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑线是条复辟线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱要举起批判的锄和锨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把它连根铲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持斗争就前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路线教育松一松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想麻痹就停顿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路线教育抓得紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持斗争就前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争哲学永不丢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨人的脾气就爱斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七斗八斗不停休！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得阶级敌人垮了台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得孔孟之道发了臭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得高山低了头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得河水让了路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得七沟八梁变了样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗得农林牧副大丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗出社会主义新大寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗出一条革命路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的基本路线记心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争哲学永不丢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺队的干部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山变地变产量变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺队的干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人民本色没有变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年老的不褪革命色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的红色日日添，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是社会主义的庄稼汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站得高　看得远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有站得高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能风格高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有看得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才有大贡献。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条　件"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条件好，利用它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条件差，改造它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧抓大事促大干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条件就会起变化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上常反骄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上不反骄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会摔大跤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上常反骄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想步步高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三　不　丢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食打得多了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窝窝头里要掺点糠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭节约的风尚永不丢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机械化程度高了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩上还要压扁担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦创业的精神永不丢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争取得了胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要看到胜利后的斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命的思想永不丢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有高峰在前头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下山容易上山难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上得山来景更宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说此山无人到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有高峰在前头。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}